{"tid":725979,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【乘客小心！】狂徒又出現 裕民坊九巴再被𠝹凳","createTime":"2018-07-02T05:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T06:07:16.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"826b7fe8bcedf1761aa1884948020f44609fd220","tid":725979,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T05:04:43.000Z","msg":"九巴接連發生暗藏鐵針及鎅櫈事件，而當中101線有座位被鎅爛。今日同一車站同一路線又有同樣事件。清晨5時許，觀塘裕民坊巴士總站，一輛九巴101號線隧道巴士，車長開工檢查時，發現下層三張座位被利器鎅爛，包括兩張關愛座在內，遭鎅開約4吋左右，於是通知站長報警。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息稱，該輛巴士昨日行駛23M線，收車後停在裕民坊巴士總站，今早轉行101線。警方將案列刑事毀壞案調查。昨日中午12時許，另一名車長在上述巴士站，準備駕駛101線巴士載客，巡查時發現上層有3個座椅墊被鎅爛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/02/130432_402cdbf927a8c83f5e625affd9e6ad58.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F02%2F130432_402cdbf927a8c83f5e625affd9e6ad58.png&h=4374a05b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/02/130433_90bb23637fe32599b6bb01651aadb613.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F02%2F130433_90bb23637fe32599b6bb01651aadb613.png&h=632bbba7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180702/58389458\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180702%2F58389458&d=cI%2B3Qi0TrAcke%2F3mYbCswB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=41abbc5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180702%2F58389458&h=ff0e9123\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180702/58389458</a>"},{"pid":"be431f05e644fb6b2add648fd93acf5d01090deb","tid":725979,"uid":26003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T05:27:51.000Z","msg":"連登反廢老力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae7a4a68f38